Package: ResistanceGA2
Title: Optimize Resistance Surfaces Using Genetic Algorithms
Version: 1.1.9
Authors@R: person(given = "Bill", family = "Peterman", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "peterman.73@osu.edu")
Description: Provides functions to optimize resistance surfaces using
    Genetic Algorithms. Continuous and categorical surfaces can be
    optimized, and multiple surfaces can be simultaneously optimized to
    create novel resistance surfaces. Resistance distances can be
    calculated via Circuitscape run in Julia or via the gdistance package.
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1),
    terra (>= 1.7-0)
